ai-patthana13.19:0.2_0: Living in the teaching, they wake up to sleep.
ai-patthana13.19:1.1_0: The support is not the ear ... nose ... tongue ... body ...
ai-patthana13.19:1.1_1: Nose consciousness arises dependent on the past. The support is a condition for the future.
ai-patthana13.19:1.1_2: Passing in the past, future, or present.
ai-patthana13.19:1.1_3: Passing in the past, future, or present. Contact is a condition for the arising of the past.
ai-patthana13.19:1.1_4: Passing in the past, future, or present.
ai-patthana13.19:1.1_5: Passing in the past, future, or present. Contact is a condition for the arising of what.
ai-patthana13.19:1.1_6: Passing the past, future, or present. Nor do they arise because of the past, future, or present.
ai-patthana13.19:2.1_0: Taking letting go, ninety things are uneven for the sake of which they don’t stay.
